thread.title: BRIEF-India's ICICI Prudential Life Insurance Dec Qtr Profit Rises

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-India's ICICI Prudential Life Insurance Dec Qtr Profit Rises

organizations.name: icici prudential life insurance company ltd

text:
Jan 19 (Reuters) - Icici Prudential Life Insurance Company Ltd:
* DEC QUARTER NET PROFIT 4.52 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS PROFIT OF 4.50 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* DEC QUARTER NET PREMIUM INCOME 67.95 BILLION RUPEES VERSUS 56.98 BILLION RUPEES LAST YEAR
* AS AT DEC 31, TOTAL ASSETS UNDER MANAGEMENT OF CO WAS 1.38 TRLN RUPEES Source text - bit.ly/2DvOKra Further company coverage:
